pr_title: Implement UringSystem and FS2 Sockets using netty io_uring API
pr_body:
This pull request aims to adapt reusable code from Scala Native to Scala JVM. To provide compatibility with the uring library in JVM, we want to import functions from the Netty io_uring (https://github.com/netty/netty-incubator-transport-io_uring).

Plan: 
- [x] Copy all the reusable code from Native to JVM
- [x] Import all the Netty functions for compatibility with the uring library
- [x] Reimplement the Native code in Scala JVM using Netty
  - [x] Implement UringSystem
  - [x] Implement UringSocket
  - [x] Implement UringSocketGroup
  - [x] Implement UringNetwork
